        "committer": {
          "name": "Fan Yong",
          "email": "yong.fan@whamcloud.com",
          "date": "2012-08-05 15:59:38.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-1648 llog: prevent journal to restart for llog cancel",
        "message": "LU-1648 llog: prevent journal to restart for llog cancel\n\nJournal credit for llog cancel should include the blocks for\ndeleting the inode. Otherwise the journal handle may need to\nbe restarted during the transaction for more credit. Then it\nmay be blocked with holding llog_handle::lgh_lock, which may\ncause deadlock with other llog operations those have started\njournal handle but waiting for the llog_handle::lgh_lock.\n\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <yong.fan@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I157093cbe9e625715ec033f59dde325e81ec6b71\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
